According to a report by Intel Market Research, the global Mobile Pet Grooming Service market was valued at USD 1.71 billion in 2025 and is projected to grow from USD 1.87 billion in 2026 to USD 3.10 billion by 2034, exhibiting a CAGR of 9.0% during the forecast period. The market is expanding rapidly as pet owners increasingly seek convenient, professional, and stress-free grooming services delivered directly to their homes. Rising pet ownership, growing disposable incomes, and the continued trend of pet humanization are encouraging consumers to invest more in premium pet wellness services, creating strong growth opportunities for mobile grooming providers worldwide.
